  <acronym>PICS</acronym>
  <official_title>The Effect of Certolizumab Pegol in Combination With Methotrexate on MRI Synovitis and Bone Edema and Patient Reported Outcomes as Measured Using an Automated Visit Manager System in Moderate to Severe Rheumatoid Arthritis Patients</official_title>
