  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether Certolizumab pegol can rapidly reduce the
      inflammatory changes and inhibit erosions on hand and wrist MRI in patients with active
      moderate to severe rheumatoid arthritis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of this study is to evaluate the efficacy of CSP used in combination
      with MTX in patients with active moderate to severe RA by evaluating change from baseline in
      synovitis and bone edema MRI scores at week 6.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
