  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  moderate to severe RA (DAS &gt; 4.4)

          -  at least two swollen and tender joints in one of the hand/ wrist

          -  patients must have failed at least one non-biologic or biologic DMARDs

          -  currently receiving MTX therapy

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  concomitant diseases or pathological conditions that could interfere and impact the
             assessment of the study treatment
      </textblock>
